 2. Consists largely of taxes on telephone services, tires, coal, nuclear fuel,
     and trucks, and of refunds other than those for alcoholic beverages and 
     tobacco.
 3. Consists largely of fines, fees, and royalties other than those associated 
     with the Outer Continental Shelf.
